divs: Sighting DetailsI was Driving Route 10 East, at the intersection of Franklin Avenue in denville, New Jersey at 5.55am aprox. I saw a Grey Oval Object with white bright lights at the beginnig and at the end of the UFO that was stationary behind a Gas station, suddenly the object descent. After that I could not see it anymore.
